topic.title: Modbus Points List and SNMP MIB

body.p: Each WaveStar Infinity system has a single consolidated Modbus Points List and SNMP MIB that matches the PDU’s customized sensor board configuration. The custom Modbus Points List and SNMP MIB can be downloaded with a browser logged in (as an administrator) to WaveStar Infinity. See section 3.3, “Downloading the Modbus Points List and SNMP MIB,” in WaveStar Infinity Monitoring System, Setup and Operation P-164001106.
